cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.CY

This paper discusses the representation and management of scientific research objects, which involves issues related to digital libraries (cs.DL), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), and cybernetics (cs.CY). The use of the Semantic Web and the OAI-ORE data model also suggests a focus on knowledge representation and ontology (cs.AI) as well. However, given the emphasis on scientific research practices and data management, the aforementioned categories are more relevant.
